    {
      "id": "6a07f5a4cc0d853a3987df8f",
      "text": "からまりしろ",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778906535,
      "updated": 1778906535
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07f5a600000000009b55fa",
      "text": "[Base for Tangling]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778906535,
      "updated": 1778906535
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07f5a600000000009b55fb",
      "text": "[平田晃久]による概念",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778906535,
      "updated": 1778906535
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07f5a700000000009b55fc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778906536,
      "updated": 1778906536
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07f5a800000000009b55fd",
      "text": "[生命論的建築の研究　――〈からまりしろ〉の概念をとおして https://repository.kulib.kyoto-u.ac.jp/dspace/bitstream/2433/215192/2/dkogr04136.pdf]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778906536,
      "updated": 1778906584
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07f5e900000000009b55ff",
      "text": "\tからまりしろとは[\" 人や出来事とかたちが関係することのできる余地]のこと",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778906602,
      "updated": 1778906663
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07f5ef00000000009b5600",
      "text": "\tからまりしろの諸特性",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778906607,
      "updated": 1778906662
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07f5f400000000009b5601",
      "text": "\t\t1. [ニッチ]性",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778906612,
      "updated": 1778907013
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07f5f900000000009b5602",
      "text": "\t\t2. ([重層した秩序]を前提とした)[階層]性",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778906617,
      "updated": 1778907017
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07f5ff00000000009b5603",
      "text": "\t\t3. [他者]性",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778906623,
      "updated": 1778907018
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07f5d700000000009b55fe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778906584,
      "updated": 1778906584
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07f75e00000000009b5604",
      "text": "[生命論的建築]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778906975,
      "updated": 1778906975
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07f75e00000000009b5605",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1778906975,
      "updated": 1778906975
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0823b000000000004b1b6c",
      "text": "のりしろの「のり」が「からまり」になった版ってわけか[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778918321,
      "updated": 1778918334
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0823d500000000004b1b6e",
      "text": "\tClaudeのこの説明がわかりやすかった",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778918358,
      "updated": 1778918362
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0823d900000000004b1b6f",
      "text": "\t\t>今の建築家は「からまりしろ」（=他の要素が絡みつく余白・余地）まで含めて設計する存在になっている",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1778918362,
      "updated": 1778918363
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0823b200000000004b1b6d",
